methods.name: queue_update_fees
methods.desc:
Fee admin method. Changes enforced to +/- 2.5% delta max
If increasing fees, schedules an update of the node+platform fees in bps. Decreasing fees are applied immediately. Return timestamp of applicability as uint64

methods.name: reset_update_fees
methods.desc: Fee admin method. Cancel a scheudled params update

methods.name: configure
methods.desc: Admin or fee admin method. Bootstrap; configure global storage except LST ID.

methods.name: change_admin_1
methods.desc: admin method. first of 2-step admin change process.

methods.name: change_admin_2
methods.desc: public method. second of 2-step admin change process. called by new admin in atomic group after change_admin_1

methods.name: change_noderunner
methods.desc:
fee admin/node runner method. change node runner address.
node runner fees must be withdrawn before this, otherwise fee admin could steal node runner fees.

methods.name: change_feeaddr
methods.desc: admin/fee admin method. change fee admin address

methods.name: update_max_balance
methods.desc: Fee admin method. Updates max algo stake

methods.name: withdraw_node_runner_fees
methods.desc:
fee admin/node runner method. withdraw node runner fees. hard coded to send to node runner address.
the fee admin may call this to pay out the current node runner before changing node runner address

methods.name: withdraw_platform_fees
methods.desc: fee admin method. withdraw platform fees

methods.name: keyreg_online
methods.desc:
Fee admin or node runner only. Send keyreg online.
Required payment if fee is not zero. Fee must be 2A if escrow is not account eligible, otherwise zero (paid by outer) Fee amount is validated against Global eligibility fee parameter

methods.name: keyreg_offline
methods.desc: Fee admin or noderunner only. Send keyreg offline for an escrow account

methods.name: protest_stake
methods.desc:
public method. locks dualSTAKE LST stake on the contract as "upgrade protest".
This blocks upgrading unless it is dissolved (redeemed & returned to user) The upgrade can also be cancelled, whereafter the dualSTAKE tokens can be returned to the user unchanged

methods.name: unprotest_stake
methods.desc: public method. revoke protesting stake for self. Returns dualSTAKE tokens to user who protested with them.

methods.name: admin_unprotest_stake
methods.desc: fee admin method. callable when there is no upgrade scheduled. returns the protesting dualSTAKE tokens to user $user. If the user has opted out of the dualSTAKE asset, this fails and the user can undo the protest stake themselves.

methods.name: dissolve_protesting_stake
methods.desc:
fee admin method. called before upgrading to dissolve protesting stake for user $user. Redeems & returns ALGO and ASA to user.
If the user has opted out of the ASA: 1) ARC59 asset inbox is used to send the ASA and 2) the transaction and MBR fees for asset inbox are subtractd from the ALGO amount.

methods.name: queue_upgrade
methods.desc:
admin method only.
stage a contract upgrade. time applicability 1 week from current timestamp. hashes are variable length, 32b each, corresponding to SHA512_256 of approval program pages

methods.name: reset_upgrade
methods.desc:
admin or fee admin only.
clear a staged contract upgrade

methods.name: mint
methods.desc:
Public method. Mint dualSTAKE lst
NEXT transaction in group must be payment in ALGO if rate != 0, 2 txns after must be payment in ASA will swap and apply fee updates if needed sends dualSTAKE tokens to caller

methods.name: redeem
methods.desc:
Public method. Redeem dualSTAKE tokens back to ALGO+ASA.
dualSTAKE:ALGO is always 1:1 dualSTAKE:ASA is (ASA balance):(global staked) will swap and apply fee updates if needed

methods.name: get_rate
methods.desc:
Public method. Returns the current rate as ABI uint64:
(rate_precision global var, default 1e10) * (ASA Balance) / (global staked) Returns zero if staked == 0 will swap and apply fee updates if needed

methods.name: get_contract_listing
methods.desc:
Public method. Returns ABI struct ContractListing:
rate (see get_rate)     escrow algo balance     escrow asa balance     staked balance     dualstake token ID     dualstake asset name     asa asset ID     asa asset name     asa unit name     asa decimals     need_swap     incentive_eligible     is_online     user_protesting_stake will swap and apply fee updates if needed

methods.name: get_rate_and_balances
methods.desc:
Public method. Returns ABI tuple[3]:
rate (see get_rate)     escrow algo balance     escrow asa balance will swap and apply fee updates if needed

methods.name: get_need_swap
methods.desc: Public method. Returns whether the contract thinks it needs to swap

methods.name: swap_or_fail
methods.desc: Public method. Perform swap or fail

methods.name: nullun
methods.desc: Public empty method for opcode budget increase
